After thinking for 5 minutes - again this tendency to play it too safe. } (18. Bxb7 Rxc3 { I should have gone for this - last chance to do something. } 19. Kb2 Rc7 20. Be4 Ne6 { Thought it is hard for me to push the queenside pawns - but
