[SetUp "1"]

{ Wei Yi has played a very nice
positional game up to this point, completely squeezing Ante Šarić. And here
he decides the game with the help of a very nice tactical shot. } { [%evp 0,7,145,321,343,336,313,313,349,349] }
19. Nxb7 Bxb7 20. Rc7 { Not only attacking the bishop on b7, but
also the rook on f8 and the pawn on f7. } { [%csl Rb7,Rf7][%cal Rb4f8] } 20... Rb8 21. Bxf8 Bxf8 22. Rfxf7 { White is
completely winning as the rooks are too active and Black's pieces are too
passive. Bg4 is also coming and Wei Yi won very quickly. } 1-0


