{ [%evp 0,2,-53,-221,-192] White is a pawn down and the situation is unpleasant,
but the game is still within the margins of equality. Unfortunately, here
Irene completely forgot about her knight on h4. }
21. c4?? (21. Qxg4 Bxg4 22. c4 { Still gives quite reasonable drawing chances, with optimal play. }) 21... Qxh4 { Okay, this is technically not a piece blunder, but after } 22. gxh3 Qxh3 { Black was completely winning and Irene had no chance of saving the game. } 0-1


