[FEN "6k1/pprbQ2p/4p1p1/7q/3PP3/3B1N2/P3KP1P/8 b - - 0 30"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Maxime has played a very aggressive and creative game, sacrificing an
exchange, but constantly posing Polina some serious problems. In the given
position, the queen on e7 is very annoying and Polina only had seconds left on
her clock. }
30... Bb5?? { [%emt 0:00:15] This move is just a blunder. } (30... Qa5 { Defending the rook, was the only way to stay in the game, although White
still has practical compensation. }) 31. Qd8+ { And next Rc7 comes with check,
so Polina resigned. } 1-0


