[SetUp "1"]

{ In this encounter, Deac has played a perfect positional game and obtained a
winning endgame in which seemingly nothing can go wrong. Alas, as long as
there are knight on the board, things can happen - and Deac made a horrible
blunder on the next move. }
59. Bb3?? { [%emt 0:00:04] Anything else was
winning. } 59... Bc7+ { [%emt 0:00:01] } 60. Nd6 { [%emt 0:00:03] This is forced. } (60. Kf5 { Maybe Deac thought he could escape with the king to e6, but alas: } 60... Nd4#) 60... Bxd6+ { [%emt 0:00:01] And suddenly Black was probably winning, although
with so little pawns on the board it was always going to be difficult, so Deac
had no trouble holding the game. } 1/2-1/2


