should be able to hold with best play. Alas, in this particular moment,
Daultye-Cornette made a horrible blunder. }
38... g6?? { [%emt 0:00:01] } (38... Kg8 { And the game goes on. } 39. Rc8+ Rd8) 39. Rc6 { [%emt 0:00:02] This wins
the g6 pawn. } 39... Qh2 { [%emt 0:00:05] } 40. hxg6+ { [%emt 0:00:01] and Indjiæ went
