{ Bardiya has been on point the entire season, so it is not surprising that he
didn't miss the following tactical shot available to Black in this position. }
21... Nb3 { [%emt 0:00:00] A tremendous diversion of the
knight on d4. } { [%cal Gd7b5,Rb3a1] } 22. Nxb3 { [%emt 0:00:04] } (22. Ra3 { It is arguably more
