compensates for the missing pawn as there are quite a few ideas such as Nc7
and Qxf7 or Qc7, among others. } { [%cal Ga2f7,Ge1e8,Rd5c7,Rf4c7] }) (25. Re1 { Simply
improving the rook and trying to exploit various tactical ideas associated
