the queen gets kicked out of d5 and White stands better compared to the game. } { [%cal Re3d5] }) (17. Nf3 { Going with the knight on f3, on the other hand, is not as good, as
after } 17... Bf8 { The knight is severely
restricted by the f6 pawn. The old chess axiom states that if one piece is bad
